MessageStrings: {
	// MsgHeader: ── Intercepted Fragment ▸ Origin 0x{0} / {1} ──
	// MsgSrcSystem: SYS
	// MsgSrcSignal: SIG
	// MsgSrcArchive: ARC
	// MsgFragment: FRAGMENT
	// MsgSignature: SIGN   ▸ {0}
	// MsgBody0: Terminal accessed. Verification key match at 98.4%.
	// MsgBody1: ...Unlabeled pulse signals remain within the static.
	// MsgBody2: Coordinate offsets point to deep echoes of the collapsing core.
	// MsgBody3: This node is marked as ██CLASSIFIED██, related fragments have been sealed.
	// MsgBody4: The next protocol window will be triggered by your actions.
	// MsgSkipHint: "[Space/Left Click] Skip text animation"
	// MsgCloseHint: "[Space/ESC] Disconnect"
	// MsgAccess: Access: Draedon
	// MsgStatus: Status: Partially Decrypted
	// MsgRec01Title: "[Log-01]"
	// MsgRec01_0: The Great Shriek. Unresolvable wavelengths, as if the entire universe were screaming.
	// MsgRec01_1: Spatial curvature permanently locked. Warp engines completely scrapped. Forced jumps only result in the disintegration of material structures.
	// MsgRec01_2: The end of conventional interstellar travel. Collapse of the old unified physics model.
	// MsgRec02Title: "[Log-02]"
	// MsgRec02_0: After 73,000 destroyed probes, the current Void coordinates have been locked.
	// MsgRec02_1: Established Base Zero. Deployed supporting industrial clusters.
	// MsgRec02_2: The barrier of reality here has been stretched to its limit, allowing for direct visual observation of that chaotic subspace storm.
	// MsgRec02_3: A perfect observation point.
	// MsgRec03Title: "[Log-03]"
	// MsgRec03_0: The storm is leaking.
	// MsgRec03_1: Physics abdicates. Absolute metaphysical rules have begun taking over this industrial sector.
	// MsgRec03_2: Timelines are overlapping. Corpses, echoes of the past, and subspace energy are beginning to fuse.
	// MsgRec03_3: Bizarre anomalies are now frequently observed within the industrial sector.
	// MsgRec04Title: "[Log-04]"
	// MsgRec04_0: Purging these paranormal entities is futile; they cannot be killed. They will be left as an outer barrier for the base.
	// MsgRec04_1: If this log is triggered, it means I have abandoned this place, and all channels to the outside world have been closed.
	// MsgRec04_2: Latecomer, find your own opportunities within the patterns of those foul things.
}

